<lb n="0421c01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0421c0101">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　摩尼囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>　的剎拏<note place="inline">二合</note>　三摩曳<note place="inline">引</note>　親那親
